UNITED STATES DISTRICT JUDGE
MARTHA VAZQUEZ

DATE this the 16th day of February, 2022.

CONCLUSION

For the reasons set forth above, IT IS HEREBY ORDERED that Defendant's Motion to Dismiss Counts One and Two of the Indictment [Doc. 278] is GRANTED.

DATED this the 16th day of February, 2022.

/s/ MARTHA VAZQUEZ
UNITED STATES DISTRICT JUDGE
